cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method for automatic segmentation of cardiovascular MR images using dilated convolutional neural networks. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The use of neural networks also suggests the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) category. The segmentation of medical images falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) category. Finally, the use of neural networks for segmentation suggests the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) category.
